chi / chatinfo                Shows information about chat sessions
 
   Format:
      ;chi                    Shows the information
 
   Notes:
      The Chat task is used to chat with other players directly via telnet.
         Calls can be placed (or accepted) with any user whose MUD client uses
         the zChat or MudMaster protocols.
      This command shows a summary of current chat sessions. For more 
         information about each chat session, type ';info' in individual Chat
         task windows.
 
   User commands:
      chi / chatinfo
